Directed by Nina Buxton. Erin White. Tenika Smith.

Written by Ainslie Clouston. David Hannam. Marieke Hardy. Sara Khan. Jenna Purcell. Thomas Wilson-White. Belinda Chapple.

Cast Naomi Sequeira (Annabel Tonkin). Miah Madden (Charlie Levett). Courtney Clarke (Jade Hart). Emalia (Izzy James). Courtney Monsma (Lillian Milton). Elizabeth Cullen (Tori unknow). Thomas Cocquerel (Teddy unknow). Carlos Sanson Jr. (Callum unknow). Philippa Northeast (Ally unknow). Ditch Davey (Roger unknow). Ben Turland (Eli unknow). Lyndon Watts (Rory unknow)

Language English.

Producers Jessica Carrera. Belinda Chapple. Ainslie Clouston. Mark Fennessy. Kerrie Mainwaring. Alexander Pettaras. Series Cinematography by. Joseph Pickering. Series Casting By. Ann Fay. Leigh Pickford.

Production Helium Pictures.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 8

Status On Going (2023–)
